{"tid":2180798,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧顯校長：做管理不能自大偏聽  指學生認同和理非 被政府逼出勇武","createTime":"2020-08-30T06:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T10:33:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e73541b4eb8664a91d30018dd6a0628ad98f4ba6","tid":2180798,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/BIPB44SNHRCLHGI5TONWDJJZ3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2FBIPB44SNHRCLHGI5TONWDJJZ3E%2F&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLMQ0GhOv7yEvjYTsEPvBCF8%3D&h=d28143c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2FBIPB44SNHRCLHGI5TONWDJJZ3E%2F&h=66200bf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/BIPB44SNHRCLHGI5TONWDJJZ3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鄧顯校長：做管理不能自大偏聽 <br />\n指學生認同和理非 被政府逼出勇武<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RF0XjPLGQ9jrLuvkbeam-wkOzTQ=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5RXA7754XRH3FJQHKXV2WHT2EI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRF0XjPLGQ9jrLuvkbeam-wkOzTQ%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5RXA7754XRH3FJQHKXV2WHT2EI.jpg&h=5a35a2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■劉志遠退休在即，自言去年是教學生涯中最具挑戰的一年。<br />\n<br />\n【退休感言】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：新制側重核心科「學生知識不足」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】投身教育37年、即將退休的北區名校香港道教聯合會鄧顯紀念中學校長劉志遠，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄧力行<br />\n<br />\n目睹過去一年香港變遷，常接觸學生的劉志遠指，年輕人本身都認同和平理性非暴力，但政府卻多次拒絕讓步，令他們覺得和理非之路已盡，才衍生勇武路線，後來演化成暴力和破壞。他曾見過特首林鄭月娥等官員，提出只要撤回《逃犯條例》和成立獨立調查委員會，「然後交返畀學校，其實可以能夠幫手，同年輕人傾得到」，可是政府一再錯過機會，後來事態不斷惡化。劉心痛一代年輕人如被犧牲，卻無奈稱「其實我哋（學校）已經做唔到任何嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「有人做嘢唔順利因無溝通」<br />\n<br />\n劉回想去年6月，曾有學生走進校長室。。。。。。。。。，「學生唔係唔識諗」，溝通後學生往往不會太激進。<br />\n<br />\n「任何一個機構，包括特區政府都係，最緊要係溝通，唔好將自己擺成高高在上。」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n在北區任教多年，學校很多學生來自基層家庭，劉志遠不禁提到早前政府禁堂食，令大量戶外工作者要在街邊食飯盒的事：「如果你無咁離地，其實都應該諗到。但點解咁嘅法例都會推出來？就係無喺推出來之前，做好多方面溝通諮詢。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「學生情緒地下化係最危險」<br />\n<br />\n後國安法的香港，劉志遠擔心更多學校會用禁止代替溝通，「禁止之後，如果學生有不滿，佢係咪真係會因為禁止就滿意返？我相信唔會。佢只會將情緒由表面變成地下化，其實係最危險。」他認為現時學校尚能及早找學生傾談，但若因禁止其表達令學生情緒地下化，學校便再也不能分辨出他們，「越積越多嘢（不滿）時，隨時去到一個臨界點，爆出來就好大件事，呢個係我最擔心。」<br />\n<br />\n就如教育局一再勸止學生組人鏈，劉志遠便認為這是學生宣洩不滿的途徑，若連宣洩機會也沒有，只會令他們的不滿越來越多。去年學生在校門外築人鏈時，劉校長便事先跟警方協議，若有混亂會由校方通知，否則「請佢哋唔好出現」，警方亦同意。最終雖曾有警車駛過，但經他出面交涉後，警車也很快離開。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人責怪教師煽動學生，劉志遠反問：「係邊個煽動呢？事件係邊個搞出嚟呢？」他留意到社會出現不公義卻沒有途徑反映，政府亦似乎只聽到單方面的聲音，「不滿聲音越來越多，無辦法去到政府耳朵度&hellip;&hellip;我諗係成個政府問題所在。」<br />\n<br />\n春風化雨37載，劉志遠希望退。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6AXcOSI5x3xKM6jYy2CaWILDVwQ=/4154x1319/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H2EXYNJPOBC3VK3BQUASMIEZOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6AXcOSI5x3xKM6jYy2CaWILDVwQ%3D%2F4154x1319%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH2EXYNJPOBC3VK3BQUASMIEZOQ.jpg&h=c787f3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年大批鄧顯學生在校舍外築起人鏈，校長劉志遠曾與警方交涉勸退到場警員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Np0LduOKBFpjrs6lYlR1ORI7mxE=/866x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MISCKCLIXNCLDE6ESD3NAOXL6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNp0LduOKBFpjrs6lYlR1ORI7mxE%3D%2F866x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMISCKCLIXNCLDE6ESD3NAOXL6M.jpg&h=68465fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■鄧顯毗連甲寅年總理中學，兩校學生曾製作海報宣傳聯校人鏈活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uYXQC4K8g9OOk_CiobiOMnL07Y4=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2DLOLN7QCJG2REKM4FVVJJHVKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuYXQC4K8g9OOk_CiobiOMnL07Y4%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2DLOLN7QCJG2REKM4FVVJJHVKI.jpg&h=595d5f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■人鏈活動當日有鄧顯舊生特意帶同標語回母校聲援師弟妹。"},{"pid":"42d10ced27d00d01404d41556b4185ac22902b1d","tid":2180798,"uid":78184,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"好校長"},{"pid":"0f3a696289387924849fb4a8ad8f68c961a640ff","tid":2180798,"uid":2889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c158fc0ab0196885a686a3b881063274b91933","tid":2180798,"uid":144626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:45:49.000Z","msg":"不愧係名校"},{"pid":"fad4a164036782e911ec5b2661863664e619e893","tid":2180798,"uid":2889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"但相反聽講上水第三位既李嘉誠中學專出黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6868cf6d255647d7bd21333d8bdd1aba16b0940","tid":2180798,"uid":182222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c102d135cd6b543bd030f9ffccaaedc5581e5e3","tid":2180798,"uid":2889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fad4a164036782e911ec5b2661863664e619e893","tid":2180798,"uid":2889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"但相反聽講上水第三位既李嘉誠中學專出黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"講錯 係陳融先岩"},{"pid":"f7d8334573864f00f2f5bf46e0deb45450a11022","tid":2180798,"uid":42422,"like":3,"dislike":1,"scor